Brisket, dry.
Chicken, dry, Pulled Pork was probably the best of the 4 meats - dry.
The BBQ sauces are lacking.
One that I still don't know what it was supposed to be, another a little spicier and there regular.
A third friend stuck with his own order of Red Neck Tacos and then a side of Mac & Cheese.
This side was really pretty good.
Maybe the second best thing we had.
I was extremely disappointed.
